text: Elizabeth Dean Lail (born March 25, 1992) is an American actress. She is known for her starring roles as Amy Hughes in the 2016 Freeform television series Dead of Summer and as Guinevere Beck in the 2018 Lifetime television series You. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:Actors from Texas Category:Actors from North Carolina
